            "modified": "2026-04-23T03:44:19.696226Z",
            "name": "Akira",
            "description": "The Akira ransomware group claimed responsibility for the cyberattack on Medenet Inc., exfiltrating 24 GB of sensitive data and encrypting systems in a double-extortion attack targeting the healthcare sector.",
            "goals": [
                "Exfiltrate sensitive data and encrypt systems to extort a ransom payment from the victim."
            ],
            "sophistication": "advanced"
        },
